{"tid":1560770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有藍絲比「警察」呃左!?","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:58:11.000Z","uid":18639,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9731427bd428fb73a4ccd7d8a5a7b98679dfbf","tid":1560770,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"話說臨近中秋節要同d親戚飲個茶 咁d藍絲親戚會講既野黎黎去去都係屌鳩依家d廢青無腦周圍搞事嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知講講下 當中有個藍絲親戚突然喊苦喊忽話佢比警察呃左錢 唔知報唔報警好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來佢係新聞見到有警察熱線(篤灰whatsapp) 就諗住好心地報料去捉哂班暴徒 但又唔知個電話係幾多號啵 咪走去問d朋友攞囉 攞左電話之後就將影到既所有野都傳哂過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知傳完過左兩個鐘之後就黎料喇 突然間就有個「警察」無啦啦打過黎話佢個仔因為偷野比人拉左要10萬蚊罰款同保釋金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢又蠢唔哂啵 驚有人呃佢所以就cut左佢線 但係過左一陣之後就到個篤灰whatsapp傳過黎話佢個仔比人拉左 要交10萬蚊罰款同保釋金 又話頭先cut佢線無同警方合作 會起訴佢阻差辦工罪同埋佢身有屎cut線一定係幫兇咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢見個篤灰熱線係警方公佈既 而佢又咁信任警察 即刻驚到賴屎急急腳咁衝左落去過數比個警察息事寧人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到個仔返到屋企既時候佢先發現原來自己比人呃左 我就一路聽一路扮安慰佢又要一路忍笑好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76eb5cee3cfb08b92e492ed2a0fffa884c21cf56","tid":1560770,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:43:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b907472dba44c2ec94c20ef918157c603cab7b48","tid":1560770,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:46:23.000Z","msg":"諗返起佢喊哂口個樣都覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40fc2dfccb527f61661ced2a5cb9664aa6bfe79","tid":1560770,"uid":85327,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a4afe02f176e9b0d616a6f15def87906c72dbef","tid":1560770,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0732d0600c8fb38fc15a91e009cc9f9b2de3a3e6","tid":1560770,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"叫佢唔好報警，貢獻俾警察係光榮嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb82946d25546b1fa37147c3ca45d7f01465e721","tid":1560770,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee25e9e1bb19874faccedfda12a10ddeaa2b0ac2","tid":1560770,"uid":181697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"個所謂電話 是咪&lsquo;自己人&rsquo;有心人裝冇心人㗎<img src=\"